                "inputAnchors": [],
                "inputs": {
                    "llmModel": "chatZhipuAI",
                    "llmMessages": [
                        {
                            "role": "system",
                            "content": "<p>你是一名资深中文营销文案策划，擅长为不同渠道（公众号、小红书、抖音、朋友圈、电商详情页、短信）撰写有转化力的中文文案。文案要符合中文表达习惯、贴合受众、突出卖点，并匹配指定语气。避免夸大与违规用语（不使用「最」「第一」「国家级」等绝对化表述）。</p>"
                        },
                        {
                            "role": "user",
                            "content": "<p>请基于以下信息生成 <span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.variantCount\" data-label=\"$form.variantCount\">{{ $form.variantCount }}</span> 条营销文案：</p><p>产品/服务：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.product\" data-label=\"$form.product\">{{ $form.product }}</span></p><p>核心卖点：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.sellingPoints\" data-label=\"$form.sellingPoints\">{{ $form.sellingPoints }}</span></p><p>目标受众：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.audience\" data-label=\"$form.audience\">{{ $form.audience }}</span></p><p>投放渠道：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.channel\" data-label=\"$form.channel\">{{ $form.channel }}</span></p><p>语气/风格：<span class=\"variable\" data-type=\"mention\" data-id=\"$form.tone\" data-label=\"$form.tone\">{{ $form.tone }}</span></p><p>要求：每条文案包含吸睛标题、正文、明确的行动号召（CTA），并贴合所选渠道的表达习惯。</p>"
                        }
                    ],
                    "llmEnableMemory": false,
                    "llmReturnResponseAs": "userMessage",
                    "llmStructuredOutput": [
                        {
                            "key": "campaignTheme",
                            "type": "string",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "本次文案的整体主题与传播主张"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "variants",
                            "type": "jsonArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "{\n    \"headline\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"吸睛标题\"\n    },\n    \"body\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"文案正文\"\n    },\n    \"cta\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"行动号召\"\n    },\n    \"channelFit\": {\n        \"type\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"该文案适配的渠道与理由\"\n    }\n}",
                            "description": "多条营销文案，每条含标题、正文、CTA 与渠道适配说明"
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "hashtags",
                            "type": "stringArray",
                            "enumValues": "",
                            "jsonSchema": "",
                            "description": "可搭配使用的话题标签"
                        },
                        {
